data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Newer home built in 2020 in the quiet development of Tarpon Bay, close to shopping and close to major Orlando Theme Parks. Enjoy beautiful sunsets in the backyard and from the family room at this gorgeous 4bedroom 2bath home in pristine condition with fenced backyard. This home is move-in ready and offers high vaulted ceilings, with beautiful tiled floors throughout, extra large laundry room, large walk-in closet, lots of storage throughout the home, stainless steel appliances and granite countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms. This home is move-in ready!
